OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for Cornwall and
OL,6,Fparts of Devon, bright and sunny
OL,7,Ffurther east. Cloud lifts and breaks
OL,8,Finto the afternoon. Leaving another
OL,9,Fhot day, especially in the east,
OL,10,Fhowever, temperatures slightly lower
OL,11,Fthan of late.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMostly clear and dry with
OL,14,Fsome cloud moving into Cornwall once
OL,15,Fagain. A cooler night for some, but
OL,16,Ffeeling muggy in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
