OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloud in Cornwall will lift
OL,6,Fthrough the morning leaving another
OL,7,Fbright and hot day. Cooler for
OL,8,FCornwall but hotter further towards
OL,9,Fthe east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,12,Fbrings rain, clearing west to much
OL,13,Ffresher and cooler conditions. Monday
OL,14,Fand Tuesday are then mostly dry with
OL,15,Fsunny spells. Temperatures a little
OL,16,Fabove average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
